items.title: US takes nearly 10% Intel stake, clinching unorthodox deal
items.description: Under the agreement, the US will receive 433.3 million shares of common stock — representing 9.9% of the fully diluted common shares in Intel — according to a statement from the company.

items.title: Yes Bank gets RBI nod for SMBC to acquire up to 24.99% stake
items.description: The stake purchase, first disclosed on May 9, 2025, involves SMBC acquiring 20% in Yes Bank through a secondary transaction — including 13.19% from State Bank of India and a combined 6.81% from seven other banks
